title: Quiz: Where's Sarah on the Ontario County Fall Foliage Trail?
text:
Hey families, looking for some fall fun? Go in search of Democrat and Chronicle reporter Sarah Taddeo along the Fall Foliage Trail in Ontario County on Saturday, Oct. 17. Find her and get a prize! For hints, follow Sarah on Twitter @sjtaddeo. Pick up an Ontario County Historical Society Fall Foliage Trail map at OCHS.org , or at the following locations: Ontario County Historical Museum, Naples Community Library, Arbor Hill Winery, Canandaigua Chamber of Commerce, Geneva Historical Society or Canandaigua National Bank in Brighton, Canandaigua, Honeoye Falls, Pittsford or Victor. Your $20 donation benefits the historical society.
Take the quiz: Where's Sarah?
Don't forget to snap your own pictures along the trail â€” the Ontario County Historical Society is running a photo contest! Read the details on the Fall Foliage map.
STADDEO@Gannett.com
